Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.38,1:23:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, you have the same brain as an animal
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.03,1:23:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you're a human being.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.89,1:23:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain of a person below 200 reacts like an animal.
