Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.30,1:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This arrow shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.72,1:24:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, the slow track is through reason and the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.85,1:24:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The fast track is through the emotional centers.
