Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.92,1:24:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,reacts via their thalamus, their left brain, their linear,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.38,1:24:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,fight or flight, alarm resistance, stress to the thalamus.
