Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.92,1:24:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just going out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.39,1:24:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're prone to disease
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.47,1:24:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're all throwing out their neurotransmitters.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.00,1:24:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And they run out of serotonin.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.98,1:24:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So this results in impairment of the neurotransmitters.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.14,1:24:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Above level 200 now, a new energy begins to flow,
