Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.68,1:25:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the frequencies and vibrations above 200
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.46,1:25:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is so high that the protoplasmic brain
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.50,1:25:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot respond that fast.
